snippet.title: The Book of The DEAD (Gameplay)
snippet.description:
This is a story where you are a Grim Reaper.  On the night of the 31st of October (Halloween) every year, Grim Reaper gets a chance to save only one person.  Get to know all of the characters by hearing their stories and make your choice.  Only on itch.io

Play here: https://35th.itch.io/the-book-of-the-dead
